item.title: Haruka Tone
item.description:
Haruka Tone

Many people may perceive Haruka as a quiet girl, do not let this blind you. Haruka actually describes herself as a person who loves to break the status quo, break the rules, and be loud. She loves to explore the world and make nature her own.

item.title: Boom Tongsamui
item.description:
Boom Tongsamui

Probably known as the clown of the Class of 2017, Boom has always enjoyed making people laugh, being cheerful and silly, but also doing embarrassing things. Boom believes if you do not believe something is embarrassing, you can have the time of your life.
